column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) IS NOT # EXEC spExecuteSQL #'< a target = INFO href = http://skyserver.sdss.org/DR1#/en/tools/explore/obj.aspx? id = # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #> #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #< /a> # as objID, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_z, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z, p.sciencePrimary, r.petroRad_u, r.petroRadErr_u, r.petroRad_g, r.petroRadErr_g, r.petroRad_r, r.petroRadErr_r, r.petroRad_i, r.petroRadErr_i, r.petroRad_z, r.petroRadErr_z, r.petroR5#_u, r.petroR5#_g, r.petroR5#_r, r.petroR5#_i, r.petroR5#_z, r.petroR9#_u, r.petroR9#_g, r.petroR9#_r, r.petroR9#_i, r.petroR9#_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN SpecPhotoAll p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN PhotoObjAll r ON r.objID = p.objID ORDER by x.up_id ##', @log = #, @filter = #
